          Insert a Checkbox.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>This button allows a user to insert a check box.</para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>


      
      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/button-list.png"></inlinegraphic>
          Insert a List.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>This button allows a user to insert a list.</para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/button-combo.png"></inlinegraphic>
          Insert a Combo Box
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>This allows a user to insert a Combo Box.</para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>


      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/button-line.png"></inlinegraphic>
